    "description": "The TecSec Armored Card is a cryptographic module which provides enterprise personnel identification, persistent data security for data in transit and at rest, with additional support for physical/logical/functional/content authorization. The Chip is part of a dual-chip PIV smart card that is fully compliant with the end-point service specified in SP800-73-1. This Chip provides the contactless functionality leveraging a common robust identity process in support of the federation platform capabilities of the overall card.",
